â†’ Loop through characters, check if in "aeiou".

Palindrome check
â†’ Compare string with its reverse.

Character frequency
â†’ Use a dictionary (dict.get(char, 0) + 1).

Medium

First non-repeating character
â†’ Count occurrences, then return the first with count 1.

Word with max frequency in sentence
â†’ Split sentence â†’ dictionary count â†’ max().

Merge two dictionaries
â†’ Use {**dict1, **dict2} or .update().

Sort dictionary by values
â†’ Use sorted(dict.items(), key=lambda x: x[1]).